<p>It's an exciting start to the year for us as today saw us launch our very first mobile app! The <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.mycaribbeanoffers.app" target="_blank">My Caribbean Offers app</a> is now available on <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.mycaribbeanoffers.app" target="_blank">Google Play</a>.</p>
<p>The <a href="http://www.mycaribbeanoffers.com/" target="_blank">website</a> uses Drupal 7 and the app is built using the Open Source framework <a href="http://phonegap.com/" target="_blank">PhoneGap</a>.</p>
<p>We're using a number of modules including <a href="https://drupal.org/project/services" target="_blank">Services</a>, <a href="https://drupal.org/project/geofield" target="_blank">GeoField</a>, <a href="https://drupal.org/project/geocoder" target="_blank">GeoCoder</a>, <a href="https://drupal.org/project/staticmap" target="_blank">Static Map</a> as well as our own custom modules.</p>
<p>We'll go into more detail in the next few follow up posts but for now please download the app and provide any comments below.</p>
